data.description: *Unicorn Alert* 2bed/2bath lake front, end-unit in the heart of Cary! This gorgeous owner-occupied condo is truly one of a kind. Offering: Stunning unobstructed lake views; Ample natural light with windows on all 4 sides; Beautiful wide plank engineered hardwoods; Stone tile work; Wood buring fireplace; Updated kitchen countertops & SS appliances; Two covered porches; Parking lot level = minimal stairs; A community walking trail & lakeside pool; and much more!
